-- U.K. Stocks Pare Gains; FTSE 100 Index Is Little Changed
-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 2012-07-27T07:49:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-27/u-k-stocks-pare-gains-ftse-100-index-is-little-changed.html
U.K. stocks pared gains, leaving the
FTSE 100 Index up 0.1 percent to 5,576.67 at 8:48 a.m. in
London. The gauge earlier rose as much as 0.4 percent.  Stocks rallied yesterday after European Central Bank
President  Mario Draghi  said policymakers will act to preserve
the euro.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
